test.name: Send a SIT 145 message to the ALMCC for an Albanian coded ELT(DT) with FGB message bits 113 – 114 = 00 and bits 115 – 117 = 001 (invalid value), other message bits valid, and DOA position in Libya. Expected result: the ALMCC sends a SIT 185 Initial Located Alert to Libya with DOA position that notes the unreliable beacon message and does not send an NOCR to the SPMCC nor an alert intended to the LADR (since the beacon message is not usable).
test.description: Expected result: the ALMCC sends a SIT 185 Initial Located Alert to Libya with DOA position that notes the unreliable beacon message and does not send an NOCR to the SPMCC nor an alert intended to the LADR (since the beacon message is not usable).
